PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777521849
OL,3,CLeukaemia treatment could boost
OL,4,Csurvival and quality of life ` Great
OL,5,COrmond St
OL,7,FLed by doctors at Great Ormond Street
OL,8,FHospital (Gosh), the study found
OL,9,Fchildren and young people with
OL,10,Frelapsed acute lymphoblastic leukaemia
OL,11,F(ALL) can be treated safely with
OL,12,Fsignificantly less intensive
OL,13,Fchemotherapy.
OL,15,FThe UKALL Rel2020 study, published in
OL,16,Fthe journal Leukemia, involved
OL,17,Fyoungsters having less intensive
OL,18,Fchemotherapy before moving on to
OL,19,Fblinatumomab, a targeted immunotherapy
OL,20,Fthat tells the immune system to attack
OL,21,Fleukaemia cells.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777521849
OL,3,CLeukaemia treatment could boost
OL,4,Csurvival and quality of life ` Great
OL,5,COrmond St
OL,7,FSome 188 children and young people
OL,8,Faged one to 24 were included in the
OL,9,Fstudy, taken from 25 UK paediatric
OL,10,Fcancer centres between 2020 and 2024.
OL,12,FThe new approach achieved remission
OL,13,Frates of 92% while long-term survival
OL,14,F(82% after three years) was comparable
OL,15,Fto children on more intensive
OL,16,Ftraditional treatment plans.
OL,18,FNo patients died during the early
OL,19,Fphase of treatment, which experts said
OL,20,Frepresents a big leap forward in care.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
