OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777521849
OL,3,CLeukaemia treatment could boost
OL,4,Csurvival and quality of life ` Great
OL,5,COrmond St
OL,7,FALL is the most common childhood
OL,8,Fcancer, with around 400 new cases each
OL,9,Fyear in the UK.
OL,11,FAlthough cure rates for newly
OL,12,Fdiagnosed disease are high, the cancer
OL,13,Fcoming back remains an issue.
OL,15,FDr David O'Connor, consultant in
OL,16,Fpaediatric haematology at Gosh, said
OL,17,Fof the study: "This approach marks a
OL,18,Fmajor step forward in developing
OL,19,Fkinder treatments for children with
OL,20,Frelapsed cancer.
OL,26,@yD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777521849
OL,3,CLeukaemia treatment could boost
OL,4,Csurvival and quality of life ` Great
OL,5,COrmond St
OL,7,F"The early phase of treatment has
OL,8,Ftraditionally carried significant
OL,9,Frisks.
OL,11,F"By using lower-intensity chemotherapy
OL,12,Fand moving rapidly to blinatumomab, we
OL,13,Fwere able to eliminate treatment-
OL,14,Frelated deaths without compromising
OL,15,Feffectiveness."
OL,17,FRomyn Winters was two when her parents
OL,18,Fnoticed that she was unable to walk
OL,19,Fproperly.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
