OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777521849
OL,3,CLeukaemia treatment could boost
OL,4,Csurvival and quality of life ` Great
OL,5,COrmond St
OL,7,FHer parents, Lisa and John, from
OL,8,FDunbar in East Lothian in Scotland,
OL,9,Fsaid in a statement: "We were on
OL,10,Fholiday in Yorkshire when we noticed
OL,11,FRomyn's leg was starting to look weak
OL,12,Fand she was crawling instead of
OL,13,Fwalking, and then she started to get
OL,14,Fmore unwell and stopped eating."
OL,16,FIn October 2018, tests confirmed Romyn
OL,17,Fhad ALL and she was taken to NHS
OL,18,FLothian for treatment.
OL,26,@qD@VOUvD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
