CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777521849
OL,3,CLeukaemia treatment could boost
OL,4,Csurvival and quality of life ` Great
OL,5,COrmond St
OL,7,FHer parents said: "Romyn had
OL,8,Fchemotherapy which had harsh side
OL,9,Feffects that made her sick.
OL,11,F"Unfortunately, within 18 months
OL,12,Ffollowing treatment, she had relapsed.
OL,14,F"We were offered a bone marrow
OL,15,Ftransplant or to try blinatumomab with
OL,16,Fa lower dose of chemotherapy.
OL,18,F"By this time Romyn was seven and we
OL,19,Fweighed up the options and what her
OL,20,Ffuture might look like.
OL,26,@oD@SOUsD@AOUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777521849
OL,3,CLeukaemia treatment could boost
OL,4,Csurvival and quality of life ` Great
OL,5,COrmond St
OL,7,F"Blinatumomab sounded scary as it was
OL,8,Funknown, but we thought it would give
OL,9,Fus more options if she didn't respond
OL,10,Fto the treatment, and hopefully she'd
OL,11,Frecover more quickly as it sounded
OL,12,Fless severe than the stronger
OL,13,Fchemotherapy.
OL,15,F"Dr Baird and her team supported us
OL,16,Freally well and kept us informed every
OL,17,Fstep of the way. After a few expected
OL,18,Fside effects to begin with in
OL,19,Fhospital, Romyn was coping well and
OL,20,Fwas able to have blinatumomab at home
OL,21,Fvia her pump in a backpack.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777521849
OL,3,CLeukaemia treatment could boost
OL,4,Csurvival and quality of life ` Great
OL,5,COrmond St
OL,7,F"Within days, she was back playing on
OL,8,Fthe trampoline with her brothers which
OL,9,Fwas great to see.
OL,11,F"Romyn is now off treatment and
OL,12,Frecovering well thanks to the
OL,13,Fblinatumomab being easier for her to
OL,14,Ftolerate.
OL,16,F"Since having her chemo port removed,
OL,17,Fshe's been able to take part in new
OL,18,Fchildhood hobbies like her friends.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
