PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777521849
OL,3,CLeukaemia treatment could boost
OL,4,Csurvival and quality of life ` Great
OL,5,COrmond St
OL,7,F"We went on holiday to Tenerife and
OL,8,Fshe learnt to swim in a week ` we now
OL,9,Fcan't keep her away from a swimming
OL,10,Fpool."
OL,12,FAccording to Gosh, the clinical trial
OL,13,Fdiffers from others because it was
OL,14,Fdelivered as routine NHS care, making
OL,15,Fthe results more representative of
OL,16,Freal-world patients.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@FO]
